<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3150249" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="2"><ahelp hid="SID_ZOOMOUT">Decreases the display scale of formulas by 25%.</ahelp> The zoom scale is displayed on the status bar. You can also change the scale in the <link href="text/shared/00/00000001.xhp#kontextmenue" name="context menu">context menu</link> of the status bar. The workspace context menu also has zoom options.</paragraph>
